{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place red split lentils and 500 g water in a bowl and soak for 1 hour.","Place Parmesan in mixing bowl and grate <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Cut aubergines in slices (1 cm thick) and place in Varoma dish. Make sure that some holes in Varoma dish remain unobstructed for steam to circulate.","Place oil, onions, garlic and green or red pepper in mixing bowl then chop <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Add tomatoes and chop <b>2 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Add wine, oregano, ginger, salt and pepper in mixing bowl. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma aside.","Add drained red lentils and cook <b>8 min\/100°C\/\/speed 2<b>. Meanwhile, preheat oven to 200°C and grease a casserole dish. Arrange aubergine slices in casserole dish and cover with lentil mixture. No need to clean mixing bowl.","Place butter, milk and flour in mixing bowl then cook <b>8 min\/90°C\/speed 4<b>.","Add 60 g reserved grated Parmesan to sauce and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>. Cover lentil layer with sauce and sprinkle with remaining grated Parmesan. Bake moussaka for 30 minutes (200°C). Cut moussaka into squares and serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["200 g red split lentils","500 g water","120 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","400 g aubergines","50 g olive oil","200 g onions, quartered","3 garlic cloves","1 pepper, green or red, cut in pieces (approx. 150 g)","400 g tinned chopped tomatoes","120 g red wine","1 Tbsp dried oregano","1 tsp ground ginger","1 - 2 tsp fine sea salt, to taste","½ tsp ground black pepper","40 g unsalted butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","500 g milk","40 g plain flour"]}],"id":"r151913","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-gEBowOdQomk\/XZVQR_wnBYI\/AAAAAAAAc_U\/8iZhkj5I6OgjFj0uQ3RKyGRr9hzQjJWzgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_K4z6Zf_uPZRlaj3v.png","title":"Lentil Moussaka","publishedAt":"2018-04-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"21 g","fat":"25 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"33 g","calories":"1917 kJ \/ 458 kcal"},"usefulItems":"casserole dish (20 cm x 30 cm x 6 cm), oven","hintsAndTricks":["Instead of soaked red lentils you can use pre-cooked brown lentils."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","2h 20m","6 portions"]}